## Change log for perl distribution Alien::DDC::Concordance

v0.007 Tue, 08 Dec 2020 13:47:18 +0100 moocow
	+ added alien_version_check for minimum DDC version ($min_ddc_version='2.2.8')

v0.006 Mon, 13 Jul 2020 12:37:58 +0200 moocow
	+ added dependency Net::SSLeay >= v1.49 as required by current Alien::Base::ModuleBuild for https downloads

v0.005 Wed, 10 Apr 2019 10:14:43 +0200 moocow
	+ add --disable-jemalloc option to alien configure call
	+ attempt to fix jemalloc segfaults on fedora 28 (RT #129101)

v0.004 Wed, 10 Apr 2019 09:59:56 +0200 moocow
	+ explicitly use https for alien_repository (should fix RT bug #129102)
	  (see https://github.com/Perl5-Alien/Alien-Base-ModuleBuild/issues/6#issuecomment-417097485)

v0.003 Thu, 22 Feb 2018 13:35:09 +0100 moocow
